dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Copperplate print. Oriented with north to the upper left. Relief shown by hachures. 1 inset: Kyōto Shigai Zenzu. Include distance chart and legend. Title on map: Kyōto-fu kannai chizu. 1 map: col.; 63 x 92 cm., folded in cover 22 x 16 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
